name: I'm Not A Human
description:
(Go fullscreen for the best immersion!)

I t   f i n a l l y   h a p p e n e d .   T h e   r o b o t   a p o c a l y p s e   i s   h e r e .   Y o u   m u s t   s u r v i v e . . . 

...SURVIVE BOREDOM BY SURFING THE NET!

All internet content is now only available for AIs. They use sophisticated technique called "CAPTCHA" to prevent pesky human from accessing that good, good content. They know how to generate images, so they're supposed to be the only intelligent being who can distinguish those generated images from the real ones. 

But you have the superior biological brain. Your mission is to pick out the 3 AI-generated images in each CAPTCHA, liberate yourself and surf the net!
